 * Editor's note: This live stream is now over. You may watch a recording above.JOHANNESBURG - The SACP's Central Executive Committee briefs the media on the political and organisational reports to be presented to the 14th Party Congress.The congress is scheduled to take place from 10 to 15 July in Tshwane.The reports will assess achievements, examine options and propose recommendations on what is to be done going forward.eNCA